text: The wheels on the garbage truck round and round..
Round and round, round and round.
The wheels on the garbage truck round and round..
All through the town.
The loader on the garbage go up and down
Up and down, up and down..
The loader on the garbage go up and down
All through the town.
The wiper's on the garbage truck go swish swish..
Swish swish,swish swish swish swish swish..
The wiper's on the garbage truck go swish swish swish..
All through the town.
The horn on the garbage truck go beep beep beep...
Beep beep,beep beep beep beep
The horn on the garbage truck go beep beep beep..
All through the town.
The window's on the garbage truck go up and down..
Up and down, up and down..
The window's on the garbage truck go up and down..
All through the town.
